went back on for my birthday with a group - SUCH a fun time! my favorite restaurant in NY for sure great for groups the appetizers and filet mignon are amazing - highly recommend and the house cocktail is AMAZING hostess is are extremely nice and accommodating!! amazing place! amazing food! amazing decor!! this place is truly an experience and such a find! you walk down an ally to get to the place and it's so adorable! the service was great and food was perfect! definitely go to the bar for a drink - bartenders are true mixologists - the drinks were amazing and watching them get prepared was really cool! definitely go! I am going back thursday to celebrate my birthday :)
